<p>[:en]</p>
<h1 id="about-cosmic-fortune">About Cosmic Fortune</h1>
<p>This is slot with no less than five jackpots including three progressive jackpots. This slot is full of features, it has two bonus games, the Free Falls Bonus Game and the Jackpot Bonus Game plus it uses the Avalanche Feature. Unlike Gonzo’s Quest NetEnt’s most famous Avalanche game Cosmic Fortune does not add a multiplier on successive wins. Cosmic fortune runs on five reels, three lines and 15 bet lines.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game features</h2>
<p>The main feature of this slot is the Avalanche Feature. The other features are the two bonus games, Free Falls and the Jackpot Game. To access the Free Falls you need three Scatter symbols. The Jackpot Game is access through the Free Falls game.</p>
<h3 id="free-falls">Free Falls</h3>
<p>When Free Falls are activated the player gets 10 Free Fall spins. During these spins every winning symbol gives one ball in the bonus game that follows the ten Free Falls. Any additional Scatter symbols that appear in the main game  activates five additional Free Falls. Once the Free falls are over the Free Fall Bonus Game starts. In this game a spaceship drops the balls accumulated in the Free Fall rounds on a board much like that of a pinball machine but without any flippers.</p>
<h3 id="jackpot-game">Jackpot Game</h3>
<p>The Jackpot Game is played very much like the Free Falls Bonus Game. You get the same amount of balls to drop. In fact the only real difference is that the board is slightly different with the different Jackpots collector cups. To activate the Jackpot Game you need three balls to fall into the Bonus collector cup during the Free Falls Bonus game. On order for you to activate the Jackpots during the Jackpot game you need three ball in the corresponding Jackpot collector cup.</p>
<h3 id="avalanche-feature">Avalanche Feature</h3>
<p>Just like in Gonzo’s quest winning symbols are removed and the symbols above fall down to replace them and new symbols fall from above the reels to fill any empty spaces. There are no multipliers added to successive wins in this game but all other features are active.</p>
<h2 id="game-details">Game details</h2>
<ul>
<li>Developer: <a href="http://www.netent.com">NetEnt</a></li>
<li>Reels &amp; lines: 5 reels, 3 rows, 15 bet lines</li>
<li>Bet levels: 1-10</li>
<li>Coin values (€): 0.01, 0.02, 0.05, 0.1, 0.2</li>
<li>Minimum bet: €0.15</li>
<li>Maximum bet: €30</li>
<li>Maximum win: €7,500 / 15,000 coins on a single bet line</li>
<li>Hit frequency: 33.3%</li>
<li>Bonus game: Yes</li>
<li>Jackpot: Yes</li>
</ul>
